'''Amand Dalem''' (5 June 1938 – 28 February 2018) was a Belgian politician who was Mayor of [[Rochefort, Belgium|Rochefort]] (1970–1994), [[Senate (Belgium)|Senator]] (1979–1994), Minister of the [[Walloon Government]] (1985–1992), and Governor of the [[Namur (province)|Province of Namur]] (1994–2007).<ref>[https://www.rtbf.be/info/belgique/detail_l-ex-ministre-et-gouverneur-de-la-province-de-namur-amand-dalem-est-decede?id=9853698 L'ex-ministre et gouverneur de la province de Namur Amand Dalem est décédé] {{fr icon}}</ref>
